				<font face="Tahoma" size="2" color="#00CCFF">
				<img border="0" src="Mr/mr_055.jpg" width="703" height="325"></font></p>
				<font FACE="Tahoma" size="2"><i>
				<font FACE="Tahoma" color="#00CCFF">
				<p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0">Святилище Зевса в 
				Олимпии.</font></i></font></span></td>
