					богослужений. Духоборы отвергают иконы, не поклоняются 
					мощам, не обращаются за помощью к святым</font></span></font></font></font></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><font FACE="Tahoma" SIZE="2"><font SIZE="2"><font FACE="Tahoma" size="2" color="#000080">.</font><span LANG="RU"></td>
